Awak sihat?

719
00:53:29,623 --> 00:53:30,457
Ya.

720
00:53:32,417 --> 00:53:33,960
<i>…buat aku rela terpedaya.</i>

721
00:53:34,461 --> 00:53:37,047
Awak dah banyak berubah, Mi-rae.

722
00:53:39,299 --> 00:53:40,175
Betulkah?

723
00:53:41,551 --> 00:53:42,385
Awak pun.

724
00:53:44,804 --> 00:53:46,640
Yalah, dah 10 tahun.

725
00:53:50,143 --> 00:53:51,353
Tapi awak…

726
00:53:54,314 --> 00:53:56,775
tetap cantik macam dulu.

727
00:54:23,593 --> 00:54:24,427
Selamat datang…

728
00:54:25,011 --> 00:54:27,639
Alamak, ada kebakarankah?

729
00:54:27,722 --> 00:54:30,725
Ya. Mujurlah api dah berjaya dikawal.

730
00:54:31,518 --> 00:54:32,519
Lega saya dengar.

731
00:54:32,602 --> 00:54:34,729
Tapi ada api yang belum padam.

732
00:54:35,397 --> 00:54:36,815
Apa? Di mana?

733
00:54:40,944 --> 00:54:41,987
Terbakar…

734
00:54:42,779 --> 00:54:44,114
di hatiku untukmu.

735
00:54:48,493 --> 00:54:51,788
Mi-rae, kerja saya padamkan api.

736
00:54:52,289 --> 00:54:54,249
Tapi api yang membara di hati ini

737
00:54:55,375 --> 00:54:56,376
takkan sesekali

738
00:54:57,043 --> 00:54:58,295
saya padamkan.

739
00:55:06,594 --> 00:55:08,388
JUMPA TEMAN LELAKI SETERUSNYA?

740
00:55:08,471 --> 00:55:09,472
YA

741
00:57:20,270 --> 00:57:21,980
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

